Whisk, Anthony...
body:
Interactive Introverts HK highlights

  • Apparently Dan spilt orange juice on Phil’s crotch a short while after the plane took off
  • Hong Kong is very moist
  • Whisk, Anthony Padilla’s remains and the essence of death are hidden under Dan’s bed
  • The audience was called Karen
  • The sims was most popular, followed by dnp crafts, which Dan couldn’t stop judging us about it
  • 38% people do not know dnp, and 6% asked who are dnp
  • Dan was sacrificed, two of them hit his legs, and Dan was horrified and yelled at Phil for nearly shooting his penis (i can’t believe I’m typing that)
  • One of the most inaccurate description of ii was that it was actually uninteractive extroverts
  • NEVER TRUST PHIL WITH SCISSORS
  • Both Dan and Phil got 0 points on Dan vs Phil, making a draw. Including all matches during the tour, they are now onto 39 vs 39
  • One of the dilemas was dan can see his buddies in lodon (hey buddy you in london? ) but phil had to be 7 ft tall
  • People cant stop screaming when Dan was trying to take off that thing he was wearing during the wheel, and Phil couldn’t talk
  • Dan had to convince people standing on a cactus and thanos was a good thing, he failed on the thanos one (cue “i don’t feel so good”)
  • Phil used to have a cactus called Loki??!!
  • The best pet dressed as dnp was a dog dress in the solar esclipe shirt watching doge taco memes
  • Dan pierced his ears at 16 and Phil has an accumalated 2 bones broke
  • Dan would not live in Antartica for a year so Phil can enjoy cheese
  • They actually mentioned Mangkhut
  • Dan kept on mentioning how moist hong kong is and his 6 hours walk to catch a far'fetched (is it spelled like this?)
  • Dan did a heart sign?!
  • A sensual whisk massage for Dan would mke him confess
  • The others I guess is pretty much the same from others?
  • They are so pretty in real life asdfghjkl

I am literally mind blown. Please tell me if I had missed any points.

Thanks for the amazing night @danielhowell @amazingphil it was truly the best night in my life.

Edit: the 4 of us gave dnp the page where there is a drawing of their fringes and dan commented that they were “signing something that is already dead”. Also we were all idiots and forgot to film the whole thing.

Well i guess rip emo hair dnp, hello curly guy and quiffed
